\ Test vector projection and constructor primitives

[ 1 2 3 ] first print  \ Should print 1
[ 1 2 3 ] rest print   \ Should print [2 3]
[] rest print          \ Should print []

[ 1 [ 2 3 ] ] [ 1 [ 2 3 ] ] == print  \ Should print true

[ 1 2 3 ] uncons swap print print  \ Should print 1, then [2 3]

0 [ 1 2 3 ] cons print       \ Should print [0 1 2 3]
[ 1 2 ] [ 3 4 ] concat print \ Should print [1 2 3 4]

[] empty? print     \ Should print true
[ 1 ] empty? print  \ Should print false

"hello" len .s empty    \ Should print <1> 5
